This is the `NEWS` file for the `perl-Amazon-SQS-Client` project. This file contains
information on changes since the last release of the package, as well as a
running list of changes from previous versions.  If critical bugs are found in
any of the software, notice of such bugs and the versions in which they were
fixed will be noted here, as well.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
perl-Amazon-SQS-Client 1.1.1 (2016-12-31)

    Enhancements:

    - reuse LWP::UserAgent object or passed UserAgent object

    - API 2012-11-05

      Batch API
      
      [x] ChangeMessageVisibilityBatch
      [x] DeleteMessageBatch
      [ ] SendMessageBatch

      [x] ListDeadLetterSourceQueues
      [ ] PurgeQueue
      [ ] GetQueueUrl

    - SendMessageRequest
      + MessageAttribute
      + MessageDuplicationId
      + MessageGroupId
      + DelaySeconds

    - Signature Version 4
      
    Fixes:	

    (None)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
perl-Amazon-SQS-Client 1.0.1 (2015-11-21)

    Enhancements:

    - Added long polling support by modifying:
      
      Amazon::SQS::Client
      Amazon::SQS::Model::ReceiveMessageRequest

    Fixes:

    (None)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
perl-Amazon-SQS-Client 1.0.0 (2012-04-23)

    Enhancements:

    - This is the first release of the autoconf'd and RPM'd version of
      the AWS SQS perl library.

    Fixes:

    (None)
